        jTextPane1.setText("This calculator is made using java only. It can calculate two types of interests (simple and compound). The formulae used for calculating simple interest is shown below.\nI = (PRT)/100\nWhere\nI = interest\nP = Principal value\nT = time in years\nAnd\nA = I + P\nWhere \nA = Total Amount\nThe compound interest is calculated using the formulae below.\nA = P((1+(R/100)^(N*T))\nWhere\nN = number of time interest calculated per year\n\nYou can contact us at ahazzkhan6@gmail.com for any inquires.");
        jScrollPane1.setViewportView(jTextPane1);

